# Implementation Plan - Hero Dashboard Hub Widget (Next Prayer & Weather)

Create a modern Google Material 3 Android Home Screen Widget (**Hero Dashboard Hub - 4x2 Widget**) displaying:
1. **Live Clock & Dates**: Digital time format, Gregorian date, and Hijri Islamic date.
2. **Next Prayer Focus**: Big prominent Next Prayer badge (e.g. `الصلوة القادمة: العصر - 03:30 PM`) with remaining time countdown.
3. **Live Weather Status**: Current temperature (°C), weather icon/condition text, and city location.
4. **Upcoming Prayer Timeline**: Quick-glance chips for upcoming daily prayer times.

---

## 🛠️ User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The widget will follow Google Material 3 design standards with rounded 24dp corners, high-contrast readable typography, and automatic updates upon app launch and prayer time recalculations.

